# Unitas-GridFlow — Cursor AI Rules

## CRITICAL: Read This First

You are working on **Unitas GridFlow** — a narrow pre-CAD QA and compliance tool for UK electricity network survey-to-design handoffs.

**Current Status:** Stage 3 complete (survey-to-design handoff working). Future stages require operational evidence before implementation.

