## 3. TECH STACK

**Backend:**
- Flask (web framework)
- pandas, geopandas (data processing)
- shapely, pyproj (geometry and projection)
- reportlab (PDF generation)

**Frontend:**
- Leaflet (mapping)
- Bootstrap 5 (UI)
- Vanilla JavaScript (no React/Vue)

**Quality:**
- pytest (testing)
- Ruff (linting)
- pre-commit (hooks)
- GitHub Actions (CI)

