## 4. KEY SOURCE FILES

### Core QA Logic
- `app/dno_rules.py` — DNO rulepack definitions (SPEN, SSEN, NIE, ENWL)
- `app/qa_engine.py` — QA validation engine
- `app/routes/api_intake.py` — CSV intake and processing pipeline
- `app/routes/api_rulepacks.py` — rulepack API endpoint

### Supporting Routes
- `app/routes/api_upload.py` — file upload handling
- `app/routes/map_preview.py` — Leaflet map rendering
- `app/routes/pdf_reports.py` — PDF QA report generation
- `app/routes/completeness.py` — completeness summary endpoint

### Tests (MUST STAY GREEN)
- `tests/` — entire pytest suite
- Current count: 296 passing tests

